<!DOCTYPE html>
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="ie=edge")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="style.css")
    title Jacobs
  body
    div.container
      header(class="header")
        div(class="logo")
          img(src="../img/Jacobs_logo.png", alt="Jacobs_logo")
        ul(class="menu")
          li(class="menu-item ") 
            a(href="") ОБРАТНАЯ СВЯЗЬ
          li(class="menu-item")
            a(href="") ПРАВИЛА АКЦИИ
      main(class="main")
        div(class="dream-board")
          div(class="create-your-board")
          p(class="dream-description") 
            span(class="your-dream") ВАШИ МЕЧТЫ 
              span(class="unique") УНИКАЛЬНЫ!
            br
            span(class="change-world") измените фон и добавьте надпись,  так как вам хочется!
          p(class="dream-install-board") 
            span(class="desc star") Установите «доску желаний»
            br
            span(class="desc") как обои на рабочий стол 
            br
            span(class="desc") компьютера или телефона.
            br
            span(class="dream star") пусть ваши мечты сбудутся так, 
            br 
            span(class="dream") как они задуманы!
          button(class="download-dream")
        div(class="photo-board")
          ul(class="photo-board-btns")
            li(class="photo-board-btn-change-back")
            li(class="photo-board-btn-paste-text")
            li(class="photo-board-btn-add-smile")
            li(class="photo-board-btn-bucket")
          div(class="photo-board-dasboard")
            h2(class="photo-board-dasboard-label") мои мечты сбудутся
            div(class="photo-board-dasboard-photos")
              div(class="family")
                img(src="../img/Vector_Smart_Object_1.png", alt="Vector_Smart_Object_1")
              div(class="travel")
                img(src="../img/Vector_Smart_Object_2.png", alt="Vector_Smart_Object_2")
              div(class="love")
                img(src="../img/Vector_Smart_Object_3.png", alt="Vector_Smart_Object_3")
              div(class="hobbies")
                img(src="../img/Vector_Smart_Object_4.png", alt="Vector_Smart_Object_4")
              div(class="health")
                img(src="../img/Vector_Smart_Object_5.png", alt="Vector_Smart_Object_5")
              div(class="money")
                img(src="../img/Vector_Smart_Object_6.png", alt="Vector_Smart_Object_6")
    footer(class="footer")
      a(href="" class="footer-link")
    script(src="js/script.min.js")
    script(src="js/vendor.min.js")
        




